  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: UI_LevelInfo_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1310c77db50a21549a77302b6beb3782, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items:
    - rid: 1154652310830841863
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 586431037440
    m_Localized: Level {num}
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1154652310830841863
  - m_Id: 1634809905152
    m_Localized: Press the Pause button \"{key}\" to close
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1154652310830841863
  - m_Id: 13029580439552
    m_Localized: "Finally, you are active!\r\nBut it seems that the state of your
      memory is altered.\r\nWe don't have much time, so here's what you need to know.
      \r\nYou are a robot, the first prototype of the TXRU model, a reconnaissance
      robot. \r\nYou were sent to this place to recover information and resources,
      but upon your arrival, we lost contact with you. \r\nThe cause seems to have
      been your deactivation. \r\nInfiltrate without being detected; you wouldn't
      stand a chance against the guards anyway. \r\nThe guards are state-of-the-art
      combat robots, equipped with teleportation abilities and capable of generating
      lasers that would destroy you in an instant. \r\nHowever, the worst aspect
      is that they possess an unknown technology capable of instantly immobilizing
      their opponent.\nBut don't worry, you are not entirely useless against them:
      you are equipped with a radar that can map the entire area where you are, detecting
      any entities present and even their field of vision! \r\nNow advance to the
      next area and remember: do not get discovered! If necessary, distract the guards
      by generating noise; you can do it by jumping!\r\n\r\nMovement:\r\nUp: {forward}\r\nDown:
      {backward}\r\nLeft: {left}\r\nRight: {right}\r\nJump: {jump}"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1154652310830841863
  - m_Id: 2542267571339264
    m_Localized: "Great, you managed to get through the first room without any problems,
      but it's not over yet. \r\nAccording to the information gathered from your
      radar, security here seems to be higher, which means they are protecting something.
      \r\nHead to the next area; we'll probably find what we're looking for there.
      \r\nWhile we're here, let me give you some additional information about your
      model. \r\nYour model has the ability to collect and merge with particular
      types of materials, transforming them into parts of your body and using them
      in unique ways. But be careful: you have a limited capacity! \r\nThe radar
      will signal any usable materials. \r\nSo use what the environment offers you
      and move on. \r\nQuickly, we don't have much time left.\r\n\r\nActions:\nUse
      material 1: {use1}\r\nUse material 2: {use2}\r\nUse material 3: {use3}"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1154652310830841863
  - m_Id: 2542293022375936
    m_Localized: "As expected, the radar detects our data storage device, but unfortunately,
      it does not detect the prototypes of our research. \r\nIt seems that two guards
      do not intend to lose sight of our data, but it does not matter, those data
      were stolen from us. \r\nYou must recover them at all costs! \r\nThose data
      contain information about our research and are of vital importance; we cannot
      leave them in the wrong hands. \r\nRecover the data and get out of there."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1154652310830841863
  - m_Id: 2542308126064640
    m_Localized: "Well, you've almost reached the exit, but before you leave, you
      have one last thing to do. \r\nThe radar has detected our prototypes. \r\nThe
      prototypes to recover are an \"Energy Orb\" and an \"Energy Transmuter\". \r\nRetrieve
      them and get out of there, but hurry. \r\nAs a precaution, an attack on the
      facility has been activated, and it won't be long before the entire structure,
      along with everything inside it, is pulverized."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1154652310830841863
  - m_Id: 2542319735898112
    m_Localized: "Here\u2019s the exit! \r\nListen, this will be our last conversation.
      \r\nYou have little time to get out of there; as a precaution, we have ordered
      the destruction of the entire structure you are in, with or without you, it
      doesn\u2019t matter. \r\nReach the exit if you want to survive, you\u2019re
      on your own now!\r\n\r\nThe only thing I can do for you is to tell you that
      the exit seems to be protected by an old model robot.\r\nFrom what I know,
      it\u2019s a model with great firepower but lacking the latest technologies.
      \r\nSo, if you can\u2019t escape without being seen, you might have a chance
      to defeat it!\r\n\r\nGood luck!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1154652310830841863
  - m_Id: 21666557273014272
    m_Localized: Simulation report
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 21666668023611392
    m_Localized: "<style=\"RST\">Simulation No. 225</style>\r\n\r\n<style=\"RST\">Objective:</style>
      Evaluation of the adaptive behavior of the AI \r\n<style=\"RST\">Simulation
      outcome:</style> Successfully completed\r\n\r\n<style=\"RST\">Simulation performed:</style>
      \r\nThe AI TXRU-00 was immersed in a virtual world with the objective of recovering
      stolen research material. \r\nIt was provided with an extremely limiting body,
      although the environment was populated by extremely superior entities.\r\n\r\n<style=\"RST\">Conclusion:</style>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 21666965622063104
    m_Localized: "<style=\"RST\">Note:</style> \r\nThe AI achieved the goal without
      doubting the reality in which it is placed, despite the oddities encountered
      during the mission. \r\nNot even in the paradoxical final room did it raise
      issues.\r\n\r\n<style=\"RST\">Assessment:</style> "
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 21667340295045120
    m_Localized: Completed the objective perfectly, demonstrating phenomenal adaptability,
      it seemed like a ghost!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 21667401762570240
    m_Localized: Completed the objective excellently, showing great mastery of the
      surroundings, as desired.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 21667421899423744
    m_Localized: Completed the objective demonstrating good adaptability.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 21667439750381568
    m_Localized: Completed the objective, but with room for improvement.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 21667449946734592
    m_Localized: Completed the objective with difficulty, further simulations are
      needed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 21667459778183168
    m_Localized: Barely completed the objective, I am beginning to have doubts about
      the evolution of this AI.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 21667471358656512
    m_Localized: An elephant would have been more successful, perhaps the project
      should be discarded.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
